&lt;p id="eVcPab"&gt;Between that and &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/7/24237732/apple-glowtime-event-2024-iphone-16-launch"&gt;updated iPhones&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/8/24237890/apple-watch-10-years-smartwatch-wearables"&gt;Apple Watches&lt;/a&gt;, and AirPods &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event-september-iphone-16-date-time-live-stream-watch-how-to-rumors"&gt;expected at tomorrow’s “Glowtime” event&lt;/a&gt;, only a handful of Apple...&lt;/p&gt;
