&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="ew1VHV"&gt;Besides &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/4/24232248/apple-event-september-iphone-16-date-time-live-stream-watch-how-to-rumors"&gt;new iPhones&lt;/a&gt;, Apple will probably declare the release dates for its next major software updates, including iOS 18, iPadOS 18, macOS 15 Sequoia,...&lt;/p&gt;
